{"tid":445632,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一個女仔去清邁","createTime":"2017-10-23T14:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T16:07:56.000Z","uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"08233ce93b968ae9a32b36f788fba43d8e640801","tid":445632,"uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"原本同行嘅朋友有左bb飛唔到<br />\n但已買晒機票住宿又無得free cancel所以<br />\n睇下有無巴絲可以介紹下啲防身防狼嘅工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外因為自己一個去自由度好大<br />\n就決定去嘅時候每日都上黎share行程<br />\n大家有咩地方想去又未去過/想推薦我去嘅係度講<br />\n我會盡量去晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後睇下可唔可以整返個post整合返成個旅程啦<br />\nps 玩四日 下個月8-11號"},{"pid":"5aed96fc87441ee41b0df8b0c1d3a3fb9fde8fef","tid":445632,"uid":22507,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:35:08.000Z","msg":"我陪你去?"},{"pid":"9d8fb1501dbfd0fb2a6d39d02ac94bb9de9affc6","tid":445632,"uid":83853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"樓主一個人去 真係要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c678f7355438ca28378a8562c3c9188c4728d9","tid":445632,"uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我陪你去?</blockquote><br />\n唔係搵旅伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c58a2528e1b72e68fbab296690eb2b5e6f9a084","tid":445632,"uid":43956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"住古城附近？"},{"pid":"d88dc1f0c3a7ca722b49bb2668a904a055d86ed9","tid":445632,"uid":22507,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我陪你去?</blockquote><br />\n唔係搵旅伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伴侶啱唔啱?"},{"pid":"e9f97324b93e1ea3ec1212afc72c44905a60119e","tid":445632,"uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主一個人去 真係要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都好驚 不過一黎唔想白白晒左千幾蚊<br />\n二黎未試過自己去旅行 <br />\n我相信會係個好好體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc684054aaa49826ce6de25952c885ed30c8f68","tid":445632,"uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我陪你去?</blockquote><br />\n唔係搵旅伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伴侶啱唔啱?</blockquote><br />\n有喇唔需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac34cc31a2f45d0d9ad04a39f520a8cc5edad13","tid":445632,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:41:30.000Z","msg":"大住肚返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef894c91049265bd3b9353a11bf6a35ddfe53a7","tid":445632,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:41:37.000Z","msg":"下年到你有bb 唔去得"},{"pid":"3f9a7ea567264804880ed9af2b912bdcd8fc155d","tid":445632,"uid":38397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"去得清邁都會有幾日join local tour<br />\n所以唔駛咁驚"},{"pid":"e450f3580829a44b112fa806ebaf6d462a75493f","tid":445632,"uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住古城附近？</blockquote><br />\n我順便講下會住邊兩間酒店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身嘅旅伴就係一對新婚夫婦黎嘅（最開始其實係我約個女仔去嘅，咁最後搞搞下就變左佢老公都去）<br />\n所以佢地就book左兩晚遠嘅Resorts<br />\n咁廢事晒左所以我諗左成晚最後都決定頭兩晚會住<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/225126_c37e27b849b8c953df1e2d0056af99ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F225126_c37e27b849b8c953df1e2d0056af99ef.jpg&h=cbcc2925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n間Resorts嘅官網：<a href=\"http://www.verandaresortandspa.com/verandachiangmai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.verandaresortandspa.com%2Fverandachiangmai%2F&d=zywy77kx8W4A4VhPRdnP2jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=61a3bb39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.verandaresortandspa.com/verandachiangmai/</a><br />\n我睇過地點真係幾遠下<br />\n離古城最少30分鐘車程<br />\n<br />\n第三、四晚就book左另一間特色少少嘅酒店<br />\n係河濱區附近 <br />\n都係唔太近古城、尼曼🤦🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n揀呢間都係因為就對夫婦 唔想自己一個住另一間<br />\n點知曼後都係要自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/225745_59a956b1c75ef50bc3fb35d44a6ca586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F225745_59a956b1c75ef50bc3fb35d44a6ca586.jpg&h=0cad0050&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b4d0216d98613793dd5e68d443a476c75d376d1","tid":445632,"uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去得清邁都會有幾日join local tour<br />\n所以唔駛咁驚</blockquote><br />\n去到先join定係香港買定好啲？"},{"pid":"d50cf8d5f8b31fd16c04cf045359a75560f50662","tid":445632,"uid":38397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去得清邁都會有幾日join local tour<br />\n所以唔駛咁驚</blockquote><br />\n去到先join定係香港買定好啲？</blockquote><br />\n去到先啦,古城大把"},{"pid":"0aa6aff1a8919a4ab54b07399d59f3be12d16cd0","tid":445632,"uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去得清邁都會有幾日join local tour<br />\n所以唔駛咁驚</blockquote><br />\n去到先join定係香港買定好啲？</blockquote><br />\n去到先啦,古城大把</blockquote><br />\n巴打之前都有join過？"},{"pid":"4647c66a21042d1b101dfc73cfb06039fb4073d6","tid":445632,"uid":43956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"唔近古城 我個人就覺得好唔方便 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76db085cf8bbbb4d23e1c55b232d876438cda699","tid":445632,"uid":43956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"唔近古城 我個人就覺得好唔方便 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724f95d8164acdc692194f5cf643b21a75dbed17","tid":445632,"uid":43956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去得清邁都會有幾日join local tour<br />\n所以唔駛咁驚</blockquote><br />\n去到先join定係香港買定好啲？</blockquote><br />\n去到先啦,古城大把</blockquote><br />\n巴打之前都有join過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n價錢差唔多 大把sell tour 鋪頭"},{"pid":"0f4a04e0dcf77cb57726ead37d3bb0435bc46de7","tid":445632,"uid":131693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:07:22.000Z","msg":"唔近古城岀入用uber好啲 啲tuktuk食水勁深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21fe5844f9dd4da1038ef55540f252c2f3fa9d1","tid":445632,"uid":90283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:24:54.000Z","msg":"係古城入面嘅話 去邊通常都係20B<br />\n<br />\n週五六日都有夜市 但我覺得星期日最好行 多野食多野買<br />\n行完即刻去嘆massage <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd281f2e006f7e2911064e627b6fd4441699b7f","tid":445632,"uid":33705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:01:15.000Z","msg":"巴打我依家係古城區住左三四日<br />\n暫時印象治安唔算太差<br />\n係夜晚D街特別多小動物同昆蟲<br />\n小強 壁虎 老鼠 都有<br />\n<br />\n街上都幾多外國人 中國游客自然唔使講<br />\n至於香港人 求其搵個夜市行都一定會聽到有人講廣東話<br />\n<br />\n但女仔自己一個真係要小心D<br />\n六七點之後無人陪就唔好去人少既地方  特別暗巷<br />\n<br />\n另外聽講國葬果段時間 有D地方唔會做生意<br />\n部分旅遊景點都唔會開放<br />\n<br />\n自己執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c00358db955c4a1537cb9d40ab840165497b02","tid":445632,"uid":33705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係古城入面嘅話 去邊通常都係20B<br />\n<br />\n週五六日都有夜市 但我覺得星期日最好行 多野食多野買<br />\n行完即刻去嘆massage <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星期六日夜市都行過 黎黎去去都係果D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a053499c8479dd4bb23f6bc279d4aa2b6ce09b8","tid":445632,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去得清邁都會有幾日join local tour<br />\n所以唔駛咁驚</blockquote><br />\n去到先join定係香港買定好啲？</blockquote><br />\n去到先啦,古城大把</blockquote><br />\n巴打之前都有join過？</blockquote><br />\n覺得清邁好悶.<br />\nJOIN 過jungle flight(玩完知好多意外, 教練安全意識唔高), <br />\n金三角團(坐車坐到仆街)<br />\n學煮泰國菜(識人唔錯)<br />\n好想去素可泰, 不過落雨冇去到.<br />\n清邁.真係好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941ce415a594b2079bc8b5cdd3b1520cdff3d563","tid":445632,"uid":33705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去得清邁都會有幾日join local tour<br />\n所以唔駛咁驚</blockquote><br />\n去到先join定係香港買定好啲？</blockquote><br />\n去到先啦,古城大把</blockquote><br />\n巴打之前都有join過？</blockquote><br />\n覺得清邁好悶.<br />\nJOIN 過jungle flight(玩完知好多意外, 教練安全意識唔高), <br />\n金三角團(坐車坐到仆街)<br />\n學煮泰國菜(識人唔錯)<br />\n好想去素可泰, 不過落雨冇去到.<br />\n清邁.真係好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用黎hea 放鬆一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4be4bb10d16cfc58e3b63ea7ba3801c024c9a9","tid":445632,"uid":104242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔近古城岀入用uber好啲 啲tuktuk食水勁深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n清邁uber靠得住嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}